  loadingPanel: {fileID: 461746976}
  progressBar: {fileID: 634745828}
  progressText: {fileID: 227989087}
  tipText: {fileID: 1903478349}
  gameplayTips:
  - "Treo n\xF4ng s\u1EA3n l\xEAn C\xE2y B\u1EB9o \u0111\u1EC3 thu h\xFAt nhi\u1EC1u
    th\u01B0\u01A1ng l\xE1i gh\xE9 ghe c\u1EE7a b\u1EA1n h\u01A1n."
  - "H\xE3y di chuy\u1EC3n v\u1EC1 b\u1EBFn nh\xE0 tr\u01B0\u1EDBc 18:00 h\xE0ng
    ng\xE0y \u0111\u1EC3 ng\u1EE7, n\u1EBFu kh\xF4ng b\u1EA1n s\u1EBD b\u1ECB ph\u1EA1t
    ti\u1EC1n v\xEC c\u1EA3m l\u1EA1nh."
  - "C\u1ECDc g\u1ED7 WoodPost \u1EDF tr\u1EA1i ghe ph\xEDa B\u1EAFc l\xE0 n\u01A1i
    gi\xFAp b\u1EA1n s\u1EEDa ch\u1EEFa v\xE0 n\xE2ng c\u1EA5p ghe bu\xF4n."
  - "Tr\u1EA3 gi\xE1 v\u1EDBi th\u01B0\u01A1ng l\xE1i s\u1EBD ti\xEAu t\u1ED1n th\u1EC3
    l\u1EF1c. H\xE3y \u0103n b\xFAn ri\xEAu/c\xE0 ph\xEA t\u1EEB c\xE1c ghe b\xE1n
    d\u1EA1o \u0111\u1EC3 ph\u1EE5c h\u1ED3i s\u1EE9c."
  - "Th\u01B0\u01A1ng l\xE1i l\u1EDBn mua s\u1EC9 s\u1ED1 l\u01B0\u1EE3ng nhi\u1EC1u,
    c\xF2n d\xE2n l\xE0ng mua l\u1EBB gi\xE1 cao nh\u01B0ng s\u1ED1 l\u01B0\u1EE3ng
    \xEDt."
